  <Strings>
    <Section>Story</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>37116</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_006_206_001</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ふぅ…………</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Hah...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>37228</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_006_206_002</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>疲れた体に染み渡る、このコーヒーの苦味……。
ブリリアントな午後のひと時、一服の清涼剤、か……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>The bitterness of this coffee permeates my own being.
A brilliant short cup in the afternoon...</EnglishText>
      <Notes>defo can be worded better</Notes>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>37832</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_006_206_003</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>私の体についた無数の傷……旅の激しさを物語るが
心についた傷に比べれば、こんなものは落書きと同じ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>My body has numerous scratches...But if you compare that with 
what my heart has gained in this travel, it's nothing but scribbles.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>38456</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_006_206_004</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>癒される事のない心の傷は、誰が治してくれるのか。
まだ見ぬ、私の想いの人よ……君はどこに……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>The one who could heal this wounded irrepairable heart,
is you whom I've given it to...wherever you are...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>39004</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_006_206_005</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ガラスのハートが砕ける前に、恋という名の炎で
新たな息吹を与えてくれるのだろうか？　あぁ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Will you temper my heart once more with the fire 
of love before it fully crumbles to pieces? Hah...</EnglishText>
      <Notes>Get it coz fire tempers glass--</Notes>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>39548</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_006_206_006</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あぁ……、あああぁぁ……、あーーー、
あ〜〜〜〜〜〜〜〜〜〜〜！！！！！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Ah...Aaaaah...Ah~....
AAAAAAAH!!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>40656</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_006_206_007</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>やーっぱ、無理だ、おらには、できね。
高い金払ったセミナーだったが、全く、ありゃ詐欺だ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yeah, no. This isn't working at all. I already went
to that seminar, but I guess it's just a scam.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>41372</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_006_206_008</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>なーにが、シャイな男が大うけだ！　このままが一番！
素のおらが、一番格好ええだーよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>So much "shy men get into women's hearts faster", pweh!
I'm waay cooler the way I am!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
